The Minnesota Timberwolves, which made the NBA playoffs via the play-in tournament, upset the Western Conference heavyweights Memphis Grizzlies in Game 1 of the first-round playoffs on Saturday, The other three teams that took the same path to reach the post season, the Brooklyn Nets, New Orleans Pelicans and Atlanta Hawks, are also meeting higher-ranking teams in the first round. Will any of these teams upset their opponents not just in one game, but in the whole series? Host: Li Xiang Guest: Matthew Watson Cover designer: Feng Yuan Chief editor: Chen Ran Supervisor: Zhang Shilei